data.description: Welcome to this oversized end unit property in a superb location with stunning sunset views and privacy galore. This light and airy property is highly upgraded with French Oak Wood floors that are carried throughout the downstairs. The Kitchen is appointed with graphite gray painted maple cabinets, white subway tile backsplash, and upgraded genuine marble stone countertops and island. Large French Slider and white plantation shutters with window casings frame the beautiful views from every window. Space abounds for entertaining with the generous living room with recessed lights and tv prewired media wall. Upstairs is a dream master suite with a large bedroom space with high ceilings, multiple windows, oversized walk-in closet and Ensuite spa bath with quartz countertops, white tile liner over the tub, plus step in shower with frameless glass enclosure and privacy toilet room. Back down the hallway is a linen cabinet with extra storage and a laundry room with upper cabinets leading to the secondary bedrooms and bath. Both secondary bedrooms have ceiling fans and all three rooms fit a master sized bed. Hall bathroom is upgraded with quartz countertops, and frameless glass shower surround at tub and shower.  Location Location Location describes this property that is steps from Esencia k-8 School, Montessori Preschool, South Paw Dog Park, Canyon Coffee, Pavilion Gym and Park plus a short walk to Hilltop Club and South Plunge. Enjoy all that RMV has to offer in this stunning property!
